name: LORE CARD 003: Alien Artefacts
description:
The settlers occasionally come across unnatural objects on their new home that are beyond their comprehension.  

These objects hint at a civilization that has since vanished.  Who made these mysterious objects and where did they go?

The colony’s scientists work with these artefacts to try and unlock those answers, and they are beginning to succeed.  Understanding is the forefront of human endeavour and who knows what their experimentation will yield.
